{"tid":2335614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長沙長期分居妻子突然提出離婚，4歲兒子生父竟是姐夫","createTime":"2020-12-22T04:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T05:03:38.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"06211b3897b33703cdfc7bfbda289109eedbb210","tid":2335614,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"李剛因工作原因常年與妻子分居，然而半年前妻子突然向自己提出離婚。回到老家後，他驚聞姐姐姐夫也已經離婚，姐夫一向溫文爾雅，二人感情也很好。這讓李剛突然萌發出一個大膽的想法，看著自己四歲的兒子，想起姐夫平常對兒子非常關心，他的不安感油然而生。經湖南省第二人民醫院芙蓉司法鑒定中心鑒定，李安與兒子不存在生物學父子關系。在進一步鑒定中又得出：兒子生父為姐夫。原來，因長時間分居，妻子經常受到姐姐一家的照顧，久而久之，妻子便與姐夫萌發了感情。憤怒之余，李剛決定以 &quot; 重婚罪 &quot; 將兩名當事人告上法庭。"},{"pid":"6ce9378fd8e4d9010e0767976740ff881ae35ca5","tid":2335614,"uid":10883,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:32:50.000Z","msg":"我爸不是李剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d055f857e7653638ec8977fd280fe14885e18fec","tid":2335614,"uid":311837,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"睇錯長沙灣"},{"pid":"c2d25b9822f3fd08585722edf5bd9c83eac35b12","tid":2335614,"uid":187584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ce9378fd8e4d9010e0767976740ff881ae35ca5","tid":2335614,"uid":10883,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:32:50.000Z","msg":"我爸不是李剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae185c2cc621c1627309b9888e7067ad74b899f3","tid":2335614,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ce9378fd8e4d9010e0767976740ff881ae35ca5","tid":2335614,"uid":10883,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:32:50.000Z","msg":"我爸不是李剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},